The paper deals with the analysis of network properties such as maximum matchings and minimum dominating sets, which are typically studied in the field of discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The networks studied in the paper are also relevant to the fields of complex systems (cs.SY) and graph theory (cs.GT). Additionally, the paper mentions applications in structural controllability (cs.SI) and numerical analysis (cs.NA).
